00:27:47.460 --> 00:27:49.560 position:56%
So the thing about the technology is

00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:54.050
that it always spurs other
innovations in ways of iterating

00:27:54.050 --> 00:27:57.410
out the thoughts that
knowledge embodies.

00:27:57.410 --> 00:28:05.770
I want to say that is was in the
19th Century and the radical growth

00:28:05.770 --> 00:28:09.740
of knowledge with the understanding
that we can understand the world

00:28:09.740 --> 00:28:11.960
and change the world
by learning more.

00:28:11.960 --> 00:28:14.130
That we saw what I
think of as the root

00:28:14.130 --> 00:28:16.430
of the today's information
inflation because I really believe

00:28:16.430 --> 00:28:20.740
that it began in the 1800s,
it did not begin just a couple

00:28:20.740 --> 00:28:22.650
of decades ago, that
was a difference

00:28:22.650 --> 00:28:24.910
in scale I think and in format.

00:28:24.910 --> 00:28:30.360
Because by the time, 1838,
